Scope of this license

This MIT license covers the original software (the Python tools, configuration,
documentation, and SQL schema in this repository) and the original curated notes
authored for this knowledge base (the Markdown files in `notes/` and the derived
indexes in `index/`).

It does NOT and cannot extend to the underlying journal articles that the notes
summarize. Those articles remain the copyright of their respective publishers
and authors. The original PDFs are intentionally excluded from this repository.
Each note in `notes/` cites the original work via DOI; obtain the source through
legitimate channels (your institution, the publisher, or the author) if you
need to reproduce the full ingestion pipeline locally.
